INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(11, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 001', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-001', '<p>Chapter 1: Why Do You Play Games In The First Place?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Evil God Gratonie, who captured and enslaved the spirit from around the world, falls dead to the ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CL3Esb6i2YwDFYWb2AUd6uQkKA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693691&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693691445&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=306&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=915343404635&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=4&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1005&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42532523%2C95345038%2C95353420%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4034129046492051&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents%26fbclid%3DIwY2xjawJqxcpleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHjHCumJ1UzZr_iAWIPKXGUouznGpz88qOjSmpkCDe5VpKB0RPnbk0-LPPbX9_aem_YiMhsWafAwDat3Pe_Ocz-Q&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=12\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A huge wave of light gets scattered all around the world as if set free by some kind of explosion. There is also a girl who looks at me with tears of joy running down her cheeks. She smiles at me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Ahh, the Spirits are being released&hellip;&hellip; The colors are returning to the world&hellip;&hellip; Thank you very much&hellip;&hellip;!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now that I think about it, it was surely a long journey. As various memories scroll through my mind and fill my chest with pleasant warmth, I leap into the air in the universal gesture of victory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Finally, I beat your sorry ass~~~!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I use the Fighting Skill &ldquo;Punishment Drop&rdquo;, a skill that for some strange reason (or a really specific setting) was mandatory to have if you wanted to defeat the true form of the Last Boss in this game, to hit the girl straight in the face&hellip;&hellip; The girl, Fucking Bitch &ldquo;Fairlia&rdquo; (or the Heroine as some people would call her) is sent into the air while spinning magnificently.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, since that was a story cutscene playing right now the girl suffered no damage whatsoever. The story progresses to its finale and the way it was doing that could only be described as the horror mixed with a nostalgia trip. There were some grand scenes unfolding accompanied by pompous BGM playing, a mixture that only total masochistic perverts would want to sit through until the very end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Why is it that the only weapon that&rsquo;s capable of damaging the Last Boss hits like a wet noodle!? It takes three times as long to do some decent damage using this thing! Even unarmed does more damage than that! Isn&rsquo;t that weird that such a joke weapon is required to kill the boss in the first place!? And Fairkus, where did you go, you useless support!? Why are you even here if you&rsquo;re not doing anything!? Begone from this house, evil spirits begone from this house!!! Or salt you shall get!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「It surely was an arduous journey, but travelling with everyone was certainly fun&hellip;&hellip;!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CLKWs76i2YwDFW-j2AUdkVoDzQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693691&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693691445&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=306&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=915343404635&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=4&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1859&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42532523%2C95345038%2C95353420%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4034129046492051&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents%26fbclid%3DIwY2xjawJqxcpleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHjHCumJ1UzZr_iAWIPKXGUouznGpz88qOjSmpkCDe5VpKB0RPnbk0-LPPbX9_aem_YiMhsWafAwDat3Pe_Ocz-Q&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=32\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「You call this fun!? The whole scenario and the side quests were all centered around you!? Isn&rsquo;t that weird!?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The game more often than not made me want to throw my controller against the wall, so I don&rsquo;t know about calling this &ldquo;fun&rdquo;. But since I was a completionist and started the game, I wanted to see this through to the end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Fairlia Chronicles Online ~Prayer of the Spirit Princess ~&rdquo; is the remake of the blockbuster RPG game that was released in the early days of VRRPG, and if I had to describe it in one sentence I would call it the epitome of a &ldquo;Shitty Game&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is by no means an exaggeration on my end. The NPCs are flat and their dialogues are boring. The Mobs are just your generic monsters and demons without any spin to them. Not to mention bugs like the party members who cast recovery magic on the enemies or use the elemental attacks against the enemies who embody said elements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About ninety percent of the storyline can be described using the following formula: &ldquo;The Heroine presents the Player with some sort of a problem. Heroine somehow manages to make the problem even worse than it was. Somebody important dies because of it. Players solves the problem. Somehow it all turns out to be the working of the Evil Gods. Defeat the Evil Gods and restore peace to the world.&rdquo; Of course, along the way you will also learn that the Heroine is somehow connected to the Last Boss and the True Evil it usually represents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then there are also your typical game clich&eacute;s such as: traps that explode every single time you walk through a tile corresponding to it, pitfalls right before the Last Boss chamber, the Last Boss that has three additional phases and forms to his fight if the Heroine is in the party (without her there would be only one phase and a different, &ldquo;Normal&rdquo; ending to be seen) etc, etc. &hellip;&hellip; So many bugs. It&rsquo;s kinda funny, because that&rsquo;s exactly how the offline era used to be.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If there was any redeeming quality this game had to it, it was the fact that in the span of three minutes in between beating the Last Boss and credits rolling, you could attack the Heroine however you like without any real consequences. It was sort of hidden gem like that. By the way, this secret scene (called &ldquo;The Most Rewarding Three Minutes Ever&rdquo;) was only available to you if you&rsquo;ve defeated the boss with the favor meter maxed out for the Heroine, which was only possible if you&rsquo;ve completed every single side quest that was in the game. Another oddly specific function that only the biggest of Massive Masochists could force themselves to accomplish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sudden difficulty spikes of encountered enemies. Shitty scenario. Bugs which sometimes could make gameplay unbearable. &ldquo;Fairlia Chronicles Online&rdquo; had all of the above elements of the unholy trinity of game development, which in turn earned it a completely new title in some circles: &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo;. I managed to withstand ten whole days with it before eventually wanted to stop playing, but then I decided to suffer through the rest of it and eventually cleared it in the next twenty four hours. After that my mind was full of the strangest mixture of feelings, like exhilaration mixed with relief.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CNSTs76i2YwDFWaZ2AUds0kpfg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693691&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693691445&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=306&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693274%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=915343404635&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=4&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2857&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42532523%2C95345038%2C95353420%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4034129046492051&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents%26fbclid%3DIwY2xjawJqxcpleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHjHCumJ1UzZr_iAWIPKXGUouznGpz88qOjSmpkCDe5VpKB0RPnbk0-LPPbX9_aem_YiMhsWafAwDat3Pe_Ocz-Q&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=39\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For example, it was like serving your sentence in jail and being able to leave after a few years, only to be able to see the vast blue sky stretching before your eyes without being surrounded by high walls.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was like being able to find the long lost contact lenses that you dropped somewhere in the middle of the vast desert&hellip;&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is only one thing I can say with utmost certainty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I&rsquo;m not playing such a shitty game ever again!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I proclaim something like that while watching the end credits rolling in front of my eyes, all the while feeling a certain kind of accomplishment spreading through my chest.</p>', 1, '2025-04-15 09:08:35', '2025-04-15 09:08:35'),
(12, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 002', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-002', '<p>Chapter 2: Shitty Games Maniac Challenges God&rsquo;s Game</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After I clear any kind of shitty game, for a while after the fact I feel like I can forgive most of the things that people would normally never forgive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CP3BntKi2YwDFbj2TAIdemAr6A\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693733&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693733049&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=328&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5272867171015&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=5&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1005&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95333412%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1924059894389655&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=12\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s that kind of forgiveness that would respond with a smile and a nod of the head to the teacher who was preaching his usual rant &ldquo;I know that it is Summer, but don&rsquo;t do anything crazy out there!&rdquo; as he assigns a shitload of homework to be done over the Summer vacation. At least he was consistent in his rants and didn&rsquo;t jump from subject to subject like some other educators would do in a situation like that. It was just like a certain character from a certain shitty game that wouldn&rsquo;t hesitate to slaughter people in thousands if it only meant being able to save the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「&hellip;&hellip; That&rsquo;s why, even though I know you are excited to make your Summer debuts, don&rsquo;t forget to study and be ready for the next semester. Right, that&rsquo;s it! Dismissed!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hearing those magical words, a group of zombies that was the class until that point was revived, seemingly regaining their vigor and energy. The class fills with friendly chatter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s finally summer vacation, so let&rsquo;s go somewhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This year&rsquo;s summer is the most important one!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am going on a trip with my boyfriend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am definitely going to get myself a girlfriend this year!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can hear all the Normies talking about their plans for this Summer, and other things as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CMzTn9Ki2YwDFdf1TAIdtTgMMg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693733&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693733049&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=327&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5272867171015&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=5&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1763&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95333412%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1924059894389655&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=23\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>(&hellip;&hellip; Now then, whatever should I do during this year&rsquo;s Summer vacation?)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Last year&hellip;&hellip; I&rsquo;ve managed to spend the whole of my important first year high school Summer vacation by myself, doing nothing else but playing shitty games. And while I was fine with spending my three years of high school playing shitty games, no matter what they are, maybe it would be a good idea to play something else, just to have a change of pace from time to time?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(&hellip;&hellip; Oh well, I&rsquo;ll stop by the usual place on my way home and maybe I&rsquo;ll decide after having a look around.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I decided to visit my favorite game store on my way back home, since I haven&rsquo;t been there for a while since I was so busy with conquering &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo;. So I picked up my bag and exited the classroom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I didn&rsquo;t even notice that there was someone staring at me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What exactly are the shitty games? If you were to ask me, someone who has conquered a huge amount of said games, I would say that they are some &ldquo;reasons&rdquo; that define them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I say that because there are a number of factors when it comes to shitty games that aren&rsquo;t dependent on player&rsquo;s skills, such as story, bugs, system, and so on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CPemoNKi2YwDFfbyTAId6OEU6Q\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693733&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693733049&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=327&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5272867171015&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=5&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2521&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95333412%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1924059894389655&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=30\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In that respect, the games that have overly high difficulty levels to them are also shitty games in their own right.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&hellip;&hellip; Well, I guess that &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo; had its own share of unreasonable things and stupid mechanics. Some of them rather huge and unbelievable. So there&rsquo;s that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In that regard this game here can be said to be an absolute opposite of a shitty game, a God&rsquo;s game with no flaws whatsoever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「ShanFro, huh&hellip;&hellip;?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oi, oi, now won&rsquo;t you look at that! A Shitty Games Hunter is going for something other than usual? Is the world going to end by tomorrow or what?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I turn around with the package in my hand, and I could see the owner of the store looking at me curiously. I was always buying games in this store, so we knew each other well enough to even engage in friendly chatter from time to time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Well, I suppose so&hellip;&hellip; After clearing &ldquo;Shit Chronicels Online&rdquo; I feel like I&rsquo;ve had it with shitty games for a while&hellip;&hellip; So I thought I might as well play something completely opposite for a change, since it is Summer and all that.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Eh, you really cleared &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo;? I&rsquo;ve heard that it would take at least two hours for a solo player to beat the Last Boss alone!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!a\" data-google-query-id=\"CL3GoNKi2YwDFVfxTAIdi14q7Q\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693733&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693733049&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=327&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5272867171015&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=5&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3231&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95333412%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1924059894389655&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=10&amp;uci=a!a&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=37\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Please, I beat him in less than thirty minutes with a weapon that was hitting like a wet noodle.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Talk about a legendary accomplishment. Anyways, Hizutome-kun, congratulations on clearing the game.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This game shop here, &ldquo;SHOP ROCK N ROLL&rdquo; has a lot of hidden gems when it comes to games they offer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Full Dive VR games becoming mainstream, the normal games are becoming more and more retro. But the VR technology was still relatively young, and this here game is said to be like a glittering star amongst the dark sky of every other VR game out there. When it comes to games, about fifty percent of them are nothing but shitty games, forty percent are perfectly normal, and about ten percent are Godly. It&rsquo;s only natural that even amongst the godly ones there would be some hidden gems that even someone like me knows about.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Still, ShanFro is amazing. This here is the last copy I have, and a new batch should arrive by tomorrow. It sells so fast.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「What are you going to do this year in the Summer, Iwamaki-san? For me, this year surely is a good harvest so far!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Yeah, about that&hellip;&hellip; I&rsquo;m afraid the shop will be closed for about a week at the end of this month.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Ahh&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!b\" data-google-query-id=\"CN36otKi2YwDFVDyTAIdJn4iIQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693733&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693733049&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=327&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5272867171015&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=5&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3965&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95333412%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1924059894389655&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=11&amp;uci=a!b&amp;btvi=5&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=45\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Go figure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I, Hizutome Rakuro, am something you might call a shitty game enthusiast, while this here Iwamaki Mana is the owner of the shop who mainly partakes to Otome Games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regulars at &ldquo;ROCK N ROLL&rdquo; know that there are times during which the shop would be closed temporarily (although there was some kind of regularity to that).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oh well, no matter, I guess I&rsquo;ll buy this, then.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Sure thing, thanks for your patronage. Now, be sure to go to the restroom and eat properly before any longer session inside of the game!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「And don&rsquo;t forget to do a fifteen minutes break every hour.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before I leave the shop, we exchange such words among ourselves, since deep down inside we are both hardcore gamers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On my way home I passed by a girl who was wearing a uniform from my school, but I was so absorbed in the game package that I didn&rsquo;t even notice her.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!c\" data-google-query-id=\"CLT4odKi2YwDFS2kZgIdokksxg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_11\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_11\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693733&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693733049&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=327&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=5272867171015&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=5&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=4627&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95333412%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1924059894389655&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-001%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=12&amp;uci=a!c&amp;btvi=6&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=52\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Welcome, welcome&hellip;&hellip; Ohh, ohh, it&rsquo;s you, huh?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I&rsquo;ve got good news, that repulsive gamer is finally going to do some major game!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Yup, yup, and it&rsquo;s the same ShanFro that I recommended to you before.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Fufufu, Hizutome-kun is a player name after all, so no wonder that it would be hard to find him even if you search.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「&hellip;&hellip; Really now, a maiden in love is truly a terrifying opponent.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After all, we live in a world where activities like &ldquo;Let&rsquo;s go outside and play soccer!&rdquo; and &ldquo;Let&rsquo;s stay inside and play some games!&rdquo; are almost equal in value.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And with the gaming being elevated to the rank of an E-Sport in recent years, it was even possible for up-until-now amateur gamers to live a decent life, avoiding unemployment.</p>', 2, '2025-04-15 09:09:10', '2025-04-15 09:09:10');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(13, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 003', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-003', '<p>Chapter 3: In Order to Boost Efficiency, We Will Do Whatever It Takes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ShangriLa Frontier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!3\" data-google-query-id=\"CPvslOei2YwDFVWp2AUd_wYo9w\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_2\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_2\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693776&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776719&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=140&amp;idt=124&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1005&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=3&amp;uci=a!3&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=127\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a game that was released during Spring last year. It belongs to the same category as &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo;, but unlike that game it holds the certified world record for the most players being logged in at the same time, which was established earlier this year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As for the game&rsquo;s setting&hellip;&hellip; It is set in the future, when humanity found a new home after long years of space exploration. Hence the Players are free to live however they choose in the game, whether it would be going full on fantasy mode in the Middle Ages setting or to bring the elements of Sci-Fi and advanced weaponry to the table.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its ratings are also very high, with Players holding the game in high regard, and the reviews can&rsquo;t get enough of it, unlike &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo; which was bombing in the reviews so much that it was a miracle how it managed to survive for so long.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I feel it would be rude to put the box on the same shelf as &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo; and other shitty games.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was a game called &ldquo;Cosmo Buster&rdquo; in my collection, an infamous shitty game from the FPS genre where the enemies were respawning infinitely and could pull a &ldquo;360 no scope&rdquo; on you without any problem, accompanied by obligatory overblown story.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was a game called &ldquo;Thrilling Farming Simulator&rdquo;. As the name implies, it is a simulation game where you cultivate crops and livestock at the local ranch at your own leisure. But the twist is that about once a week huge natural catastrophes like tsunamis or earthquakes or tornadoes roll through the ranch and you had to start everything from scratch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ldquo;Survival Gunman&rdquo; was a catastrophe all of its own, which was so riddled with Gacha that it bombed shortly after being released.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was &ldquo;United Runes&rdquo;, the game that came some years ago, and it was simply apocalyptic levels of bad. Not only was it a cooperation game without any kind of single player to speak of, but the items drop rates were so abysmal that it was almost making the game unplayable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!4\" data-google-query-id=\"CMH6lOei2YwDFS2F2AUdj4sxEw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_3\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_3\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693776&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776719&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=140&amp;idt=137&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1835&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=4&amp;uci=a!4&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=141\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>But wait, there&rsquo;s more&hellip;&hellip; Oh, guess I&rsquo;m getting a little carried away.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If I decided to go through my collection right now, I am fairly sure that there would be some really interesting additions to be found there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I place the ShanFro package somewhere else away from all the shitty games, on the table near my bed where all the systems and controllers were.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Right&hellip;&hellip; Let&rsquo;s get this party started.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I made sure to use the restroom and have something to eat and drink beforehand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After doing all that, I lie down on my bed and boot the console.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I also make sure that there is a bottle of water in case I needed something to drink right after finishing playing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After confirming those basic rules of VR gaming, I was about ready to venture into my first genuine &ldquo;game&rdquo; in years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" data-google-query-id=\"CKXplOei2YwDFcmi2AUdEvwDFQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_4\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_4\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693776&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776720&amp;bpp=3&amp;bdt=141&amp;idt=147&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2497&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=150\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hee&hellip;&hellip; So, you can adjust things like height, gender and appearance?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was a somewhat standard setting for any MMORPG out there, but still the number of options and freedom of choice was kind of overwhelming at first.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Race, physique, accessories&hellip;&hellip; wait, you can even add horns here!? &hellip;&hellip; With this level of customization, I don&rsquo;t think there would be any two avatars that would be exactly the same, even if I really tried hard to find them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I wonder, what should I make my avatar look like?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I belong to those people who tend to make their gaming avatars different from my real appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I know that there are players who recreate their own appearance because of how confident they are in their own looks, but I strongly believe that game world and reality should be two different things.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hmm? Oh, so it&rsquo;s that system where you decide on your class first and choose appearance later, huh?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apparently this game calculates your stats from the moment you are born into this world and depending on the occupation you choose to do.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!6\" data-google-query-id=\"CMSfkuei2YwDFdSf2AUdOq4cEg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_5\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_5\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693776&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776723&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=145&amp;idt=154&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3207&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=6&amp;uci=a!6&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=157\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And since the list was rather long and complex, I decided to start my avatar creation from there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Uwah&hellip;&hellip; It takes more than five seconds to scroll down from the top to bottom, how am I supposed to choose a job like this&hellip;&hellip;?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That being said, this knight (OO user)&hellip;&hellip; Aggh, I knew it! It&rsquo;s going to be too long trying to have a look at them one by one. Not to mention that after choosing a class you needed to also choose a weapon you were going to use. At first your equipment would be basic and made out of wood, but talk about commitment from the developer&rsquo;s side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If that&rsquo;s the case&hellip;&hellip; Yeah, let&rsquo;s become a mercenary whose skills focus solely on dishing out as much DPS as possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Place of origin&hellip;&hellip; fumu.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Noble, commoner, orphan, outcast&hellip;&hellip; Those were all standard options, but yet again, there were just so many of them&hellip;&hellip; Ah.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Wanderer&hellip;&hellip; This sounds nice.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My defense stats would be rather weak, but my luck would be set a little bit higher to compensate for that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"COe2p-ei2YwDFfSb2AUdLe4ssQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693777&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776724&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=146&amp;idt=163&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3359&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=7&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=459\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>And I believe that luck is going to be an important parameter, since it will affect things like critical chance or item drop rate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Oh well, it is only a game, so does it really matter? Having a high luck stat shouldn&rsquo;t be a bad thing to have around.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Next I tried to tailor my appearance so that it would match my job and place of origin&hellip;&hellip; This should be about right.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「This is&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Surprisingly enough, the end product of all of my editing was&hellip;&hellip; A half-naked figure of a long-eared man, who looked almost identical to my avatar from when I was clearing the &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo;. How did this happen?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No, there was a reason for this, trust me. It was all for the sake of getting a good start. I examined the game&rsquo;s manual and it looks like you could sell the initial equipment you were starting with. Mercenaries had the mercenary class items and equipment, which were going to sell for quite a bit of money. It was able to double or even triple the amount of money you were going to start with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Money was sure to be an important element of this game. As a full dive game, even after receiving a quest you had to go and do anything yourself, without any kind of shortcuts or fast travel, so completing quests was rather hard and time consuming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My playstyle usually revolved around maneuverability and using strong weapons rather than fitting myself into armors, hence I was always selling it first&hellip;&hellip; However, walking around half-naked while looking like the protagonist of &ldquo;Shit Chronicles Online&rdquo; was pretty embarrassing in its own right&hellip;&hellip; so I decided to wear a mask on my face, one that would resemble a bird&rsquo;s beak (&ldquo;Mask of Bird&rsquo;s Eye&rdquo;) and that would give me a slight boost to perception and eyesight. It was one of the options available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CI_jruei2YwDFUmF2AUd1mUI9g\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693777&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776725&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=146&amp;idt=178&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3607&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=8&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=621\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「This is&hellip;&hellip; No, no, no! I&rsquo;m sure there are people out there who have even more ridiculous ideas than that&hellip;&hellip; Finish!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Before doubt would force me to erase all of my progress, I press the &ldquo;Proceed&rdquo; button and finish the rest of my character&rsquo;s creation. Now the only thing that was left was to input my Player&rsquo;s name.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But there was no problem here.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was always using this name in every game I&rsquo;ve played before, creating a certain legend to it. That name was the name of the man who has conquered many shitty games! &hellip;&hellip; Nothing wrong with that for a mercenary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Sanraku, there&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I derived this name from the alternative readings of kanji in my own name, so it wasn&rsquo;t as witty as I would like it to be, but oh well, what can you do?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Now, game&hellip;&hellip; Show me what you got!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With that, a new mercenary was about to enter the world of ShangriLa Frontier&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"1271867415\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CJqJ0-ei2YwDFcef2AUdSiMfqQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=1271867415&amp;adk=652191344&amp;adf=827654039&amp;pi=t.ma~as.1271867415&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693777&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693776726&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=147&amp;idt=186&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=4905729005656&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=6&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3759&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C42531706%2C95331833%2C95353450%2C95354562%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2615520904772974&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-002%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=9&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=1212\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although the game is available worldwide, due to things like time difference or lag and Internet connection, there weren&rsquo;t that many players who were migrating servers, therefore the playerbase for each country was always more or less the same.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Furthermore, since the only available language for the game was Japanese, it was hard for players outside of Japan to get into the game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But still, the number of people playing was as astonishing as ever!</p>', 3, '2025-04-15 09:09:54', '2025-04-15 09:09:54');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(14, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 004', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-004', '<p>Chapter 4: Reality Does Not Equal Quality, But the Other Way Around</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Long ago, Gods were walking throughout the lands alongside humans.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!3\" data-google-query-id=\"COqoi_qi2YwDFfywSwUdG34Mgw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_2\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_2\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693816&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816515&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=220&amp;idt=126&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1005&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=3&amp;uci=a!3&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=131\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ahh, is this the prologue to the game?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「The great Gods spun life across the universe, and once their task was done, they disappeared without a trace.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Time goes on, the Gods that remained perish one by one, we take off to the stars as they intended us to do, and thus the great web of life continues to spin&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Now, we live in times &ndash;&ndash; SKIP. The heritage from the Gods &ndash;&ndash; SKIP. History and ruins &ndash;&ndash; SKIP.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「&hellip;&hellip; Skip.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I read that in the instruction manual.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I skipped the whole prologue without giving it much thought. Then I felt that my avatar was regaining its consciousness. I try to look and move around, getting a feel of my new body since its physique and height were different from my real one&hellip;&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!4\" data-google-query-id=\"CPDVi_qi2YwDFZuTSwUd_RALaw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_3\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_3\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693816&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816516&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=221&amp;idt=140&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1691&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;cms=2&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=4&amp;uci=a!4&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=145\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was inside of a dense forest&hellip;&hellip; No, I knew what it was in reality. Like in every game from this genre, it was one of the low level exploration zones, the so called &ldquo;Starting Points&rdquo;. The purpose of such zones was for the new players to get used to the control schemes, fight some monsters, pick up some of the basic items and obtain some EXP points. The small details varied from game to game, but the overall premise was more or less the same.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「First of all, I need to understand my current situation.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As I say that I open the status screen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PN: Sanraku<br />\r\nLV: 1<br />\r\nJob: Mercenary (Dual Wielding, Swords)<br />\r\n9000 Mani<br />\r\nHP (Health Points): 30<br />\r\nMP (Magic Points) : 10<br />\r\nSTM (Stamina): 20<br />\r\nSTR (Strength): 10<br />\r\nDEX (Dexterity): 15<br />\r\nAGI (Agility): 10<br />\r\nTEC (Technique): 15<br />\r\nVIT (Vitality): 1 (2)<br />\r\nLUC (Luck): 30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SKILLS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash; Spin Slash<br />\r\n&ndash; Knuckle Rush</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipment:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Right Hand: Mercenary Blade<br />\r\nLeft Hand: Mercenary Blade<br />\r\nHead: Mask of Bird&rsquo;s Eye (VIT +2)<br />\r\nTorso: None<br />\r\nLegs: None<br />\r\nFeet: None<br />\r\nAccessory: None</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" data-google-query-id=\"CNaIjvqi2YwDFVICgwMdp9UDxQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_4\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_4\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693816&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816517&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=222&amp;idt=150&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2857&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;cms=2&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=153\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Paper thin defenses and extraordinary good luck. Two swords for dual wielding on the otherwise half naked body. Some start for a hero.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Right, now that I&rsquo;ve got that taken care off, let&rsquo;s try how the character&rsquo;s movements feel&hellip;&hellip;!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And after I do that, then what? Since I had my weapons on me I should expect to be attacked at any moment, so it would be a good idea to see how the battle controls work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Amazing&hellip;&hellip; My body moves so smoothly.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was a matter of enough time to develop things properly. In the early days of full dive technology the character movements tended to be rather slow and awkward, but the way my avatar moved in this game it was very close to recreating the movements from reality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The system was also separating one&rsquo;s consciousness from one&rsquo;s real body to prevent it from any movements during gaming sessions, but it was certainly a bit weird to know that even though you were moving inside of the game your body was still.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Gigi!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oh.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!6\" data-google-query-id=\"CNevjvqi2YwDFa2PSwUdnssGCQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_5\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_5\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693816&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816517&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=222&amp;idt=161&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3591&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=6&amp;uci=a!6&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=165\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You would think that the future champion of ShanFro would need to battle a mighty foe, such as a dragon, for his first real battle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But in reality, the things that appeared right in front of me were about the size of children and nearly as loud and obnoxious&hellip;&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Goblins?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Gugagigi!!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Goblin&hellip;&hellip; A kind of Mob that always appears in the games with fantasy setting, smaller and weaker than a Player Character. Of course there were many variants of them with various stats and skills and difficulty level, but the core concept was always that it was a monster that could be used to obtain some EXP points early on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I watched the Goblin stare at me before it eventually broke into a rush, coming straight at me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「&hellip;&hellip; Ho.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Gyah!?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CKOtuvqi2YwDFVXKPAIdkEwplw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693817&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816518&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=223&amp;idt=170&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3161&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=7&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=885\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I dodge the goblin&rsquo;s rush and watch him getting carried forward with his momentum before eventually hooking its leg. In some games weaker monsters would die even when the slightest contact with the weapon or body of the player was made, but in this case there was no damage being calculated for that action of mine. However, the physics seemed to be working fine and the goblin landed on the ground face first.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「How about a double strike&hellip;&hellip; Onto the ribs!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Gyaaah!?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since it was virtual reality the action itself was greatly simplified to just two blunt hits that didn&rsquo;t really dealt any damage. So for a little while I was using this here goblin to try out various things I learned in other VR shitty games, wanting to see if I would be able to recreate the same actions in ShanFro as well. When I finally cut the goblin with my sword there is a large wound on its stomach, but instead of blood a geyser of red pixels shoots forth instead of blood. The goblin&rsquo;s HP bar continued to decrease and eventually it reached zero, forcing it to dissolve into a mass of small polygons and eventually disappear.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At first when the monsters would die players needed to ransack their bodies for drop items, but after it was deemed too graphic, it was a general consensus that the dropped items would be left in the field after the monster&rsquo;s death.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the dawn of the VR technology there was this serious rant that &ldquo;Video games distorts the sense of values in young people&rdquo;. If I recall correctly, in some regions it was reaching such extremes as banning games completely or at least &ldquo;Needing to educate both children and parents from a very young age&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Around that time I was so busy growing corn on my little farm and then having it destroyed by the various cataclysms that would come through my farm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「The drop is&hellip;&hellip; Oh.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CNTQ1vqi2YwDFQIAgwMd6SAMzQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693817&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816519&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=224&amp;idt=174&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3712&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=3&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=8&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=1353\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The dropped items were the only things that were left from the pixelated goblin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was another simplified mechanic, for when you touch the chest or item that dropped out of a monster&rsquo;s corpse it would be automatically transported inside of your inventory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Fumu&hellip;&hellip; Goblin Hatchet, huh?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was a two-handed weapon, which meant that its required dexterity was cut in half. &hellip;&hellip; Oh well, you could say it was a signature weapon dropped by goblins in games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s not like I was going to use that as my main weapon, but it was a good thing to have it as a back-up one, just in case and to be on the safe side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I wonder if you can get hungry in this game? Maybe it is something of a hidden parameter in the system&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I needed to hunt some monsters in the future and see what kind of things they would drop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&hellip;&hellip; Aah, this is probably one thing that shitty games and Godly games tend to have in common: grind.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"1271867415\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CKXe_P2i2YwDFZIBgwMd6GcA0g\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=1271867415&amp;adk=652191344&amp;adf=827654039&amp;pi=t.ma~as.1271867415&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693824&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693816520&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=225&amp;idt=181&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6650442084246&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=7&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=4119&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=425&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95353930%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2858199145816633&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=1&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-003%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=9&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=8273\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was a feeling that you would rarely get to experience in life: this exhilaration and rush of endorphins thinking about what to do next.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「But most importantly, let&rsquo;s not forget to enjoy ourselves!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Saying that, I took a step into the dense forest, looking forward to spot any kind of goal I could follow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By the way, it was really probable for the character to start half-naked like that, you know?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mostly because of the fact that selling items at the character creation screen was way better than selling it at the shop or at a blacksmith&rsquo;s.</p>', 4, '2025-04-15 09:10:38', '2025-04-15 09:10:38');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(15, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 005', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-005', '<p>Chapter 5: Good Things Come to Those Who Wait</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I eventually changed my location and arrived at &ldquo;Firstia&rdquo;, a small town which was supposed to be a hub for players who only recently started their adventure with ShangriLa Frontier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CN3p_ZSj2YwDFZJaDwIdsN05Og\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693873&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693872852&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=232&amp;idt=160&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=2536243661838&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=8&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1029&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332925%2C95353420%2C95353451%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3300411432638623&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=164\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was your typical, run-of-the-mill fantasy town with no exceptional landmarks to speak of, specially enhanced by the server to be able to accommodate a huge number of new players, since it was the beginning of the Summer season and all that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Wow&hellip;&hellip; You can understand that people are way higher in level here just from their equipment alone&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I&rsquo;m sure that I&rsquo;ve seen this emblem somewhere before as well&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「That&rsquo;s the insignia of the Guild that only accepts players with level ninety or above into their ranks, and only after the admission test!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I wonder what such a high-level player is doing in the place for beginners? &hellip;&hellip; Hey, take a look at that!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This guy had a fully plated armor covering his body, made out of platinum no less! He wore a cloak which housed this Guild&rsquo;s emblem, a symbol of the sword. Unlike the basic equipment of the new players, he had a huge sword hanging from the belt at his waist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Needless to say, no newbie could ever look like that, even if they wanted to or no matter how much money they were willing to pay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The other players, who I at first mistakenly took for an NPCs, were exchanging excited whispers while looking at the guy, following him with their gazes and taking screenshots just so that they could admire them later. It must have been hard for the guy to be dealing with this kind of treatment, but oh well. I had my own matters which I needed to attend to.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CMn8_ZSj2YwDFfdfDwIdINMvsQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693873&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693872855&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=235&amp;idt=172&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=2536243661838&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=8&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1787&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332925%2C95353420%2C95353451%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3300411432638623&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=176\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Now this is quite the predicament&hellip;&hellip; One that I wasn&rsquo;t able to anticipate at all&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About two hours later I decided to organize my equipment after doing some more grinding. And since I was hunting for monsters at the edge of the nearby forest I decided to climb onto a tree before opening the menu, since there was always a possibility that the monsters could attack me while I was still on the ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is then that I encountered two major problems.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The first one would be the weight of the equipment. It seems that whatever was too large for me to carry would be stored in my inventory, but when the weight of the inventory passed a certain amount, my movements would suffer a negative buff because of that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So far I have collected twelve items, four of which were pieces of armor and others were basic goblin weapons. And when I was placing the ninth Goblin Hatchet in my inventory, I could already feel that my movements were starting to slow down.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to Goblins, I encountered some other monsters as well, like for example the pig-headed Orcs taken straight out of a Dark Fantasy setting, some small local fauna like piglets or wolves, but there were also rarer monsters such as Vorpal Bunny, which was a larger, bipedal monster.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vorpal Bunny proved itself to be a little more of a challenge from Goblins and Orcs, but at the end of the day it was just a rabbit: it may have critted more than other mobs, but once you got used to its attack patterns, it was a pretty easy opponent to deal with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, the weapon it drops, which apparently had a five percent chance of spawning upon its death, &ldquo;Vorpal Chopper&rdquo;, was a rather solid weapon for the beginner zone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CMjy_pSj2YwDFfBXDwIdOSs2lw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693873&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693872858&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=239&amp;idt=180&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=2536243661838&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=8&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2569&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332925%2C95353420%2C95353451%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3300411432638623&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=5&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=185\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Comparing it to my initial mercenary weapons, its stats were better all across the board and it held an additional effect of boosting one&rsquo;s critical damage a little bit. Overall, it suited my fighting style rather nicely.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not to mention that my level also increased. It looks like Vorpal Bunny may be good prey for a while to focus my attention on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PN: Sanraku<br />\r\nLV: 12<br />\r\nJob: Mercenary (Dual Wielding Swordsman)<br />\r\n9,000 Mani</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HP: 30<br />\r\nMP: 10<br />\r\nSTM: 25<br />\r\nSTR: 10<br />\r\nDEX: 15<br />\r\nAGI: 25<br />\r\nTEC: 20<br />\r\nVIT: 1 (2)<br />\r\nLUC: 55</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Skills:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>・ Spin Slash<br />\r\n・ Skull Pierce<br />\r\n・ Knuckle Rush<br />\r\n・ Tap Step<br />\r\n・ Flash Counter</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipment:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Right Hand: Mercenary Blade<br />\r\nLeft Hand: Mercenary Blade<br />\r\nHead: Mask of Bird&rsquo;s Eye (VIT + 2)<br />\r\nTorso: None<br />\r\nWaist: None<br />\r\nFeet: None<br />\r\nAccessory: None</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!a\" data-google-query-id=\"CPq0_5Sj2YwDFRhgDwIdxCw5MQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693873&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693872860&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=241&amp;idt=190&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=2536243661838&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=8&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3759&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332925%2C95353420%2C95353451%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3300411432638623&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=10&amp;uci=a!a&amp;btvi=6&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=194\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this game, you could allocate points to statistics every time you leveled up and as for weapons, you could use them to the point where they actually broke or shattered into pieces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Getting up to level twelve scored me about fifty five points to allocate into my stats, but for the time being I chose to allocate half of that amount into my Luck.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My reason for that being that Luck must be responsible for increasing my chances of obtaining better drops from monsters and making it easier for me to score a critical hit during battles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I also managed to learn some new battle skills, which were proving especially useful in battles against the Vorpal Bunnies, which made it easier to dispose of them quickly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But aside from leveling up, it seems that there are also skills that can be obtained via satisfying some other unspecified conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And when it comes to using skills in battle, even though I have never used them before in my life, I somehow instinctively knew that &ldquo;This skill does this&rdquo; and &ldquo;That skill works like that&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In comparison, some older games were simply forcing the body of a player to execute certain actions, but it was so bad and archaic that it was eventually scratched and forgotten, disappearing from the mainstream for good.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The skills I had with me from the very beginning I was already getting really familiar with their use right about now. They may have been ineffective to use when it comes to the move set, but their DPS was relatively high.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!b\" data-google-query-id=\"CLiCoZWj2YwDFV9HDwIdgp4mXQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693873&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693872861&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=242&amp;idt=200&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=2536243661838&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=8&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3425&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332925%2C95353420%2C95353451%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3300411432638623&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=11&amp;uci=a!b&amp;btvi=7&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=728\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amongst the new skills I managed to learn is the one called &ldquo;Skull Pierce&rdquo;, which was quick to generate and it was a powerful one hit attack.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The &ldquo;Tap Step&rdquo; was a passive skill which boosted my Evasion rate slightly, and &ldquo;Flash Counter&rdquo; was a passive skill which made parrying a little bit easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Objectively speaking, &ldquo;Skull Pierce&rdquo; seemed like the only really useful skill in my kit at the current moment. The starting skills you could literally do nothing about and the passive skills were more dependent on your own playstyle.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Seeing just how well-thought out this system was compared to some of the shitty games I have played during my career, it was bringing tears to my eyes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Everything was working as it should, mobs were presenting moderate levels of challenge suitable for your level and there were no bugs to speak of at the current moment. It was really something else alright.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But back to the topic at hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another problem is that my inventory space got quite full already&hellip;&hellip; In that regard it would be impossible to add new items to it after a while, not to mention being able to organize all of the consumable items such as raw meat. That was the second problem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Blegh&hellip;&hellip; I guess you really can&rsquo;t eat raw meat after all, huh?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!c\" data-google-query-id=\"CPKk_5qj2YwDFcRfDwIdgCQMpA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_11\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_11\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693885&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693872863&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=243&amp;idt=209&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=2536243661838&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=8&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3880&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=144&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332925%2C95353420%2C95353451%2C95354564%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3300411432638623&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=1&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-004%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=12&amp;uci=a!c&amp;btvi=8&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=12757\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apparently in this game raw ingredients couldn&rsquo;t be used as consumable items unless you processed or cooked them properly. Even if you tried, the only effect you would get would be that of a diminishing appetite.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The biggest problem for Sanraku right now is that I do not have any means of producing a fire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And seeing that my MP was not getting any bigger since level one, I guess I won&rsquo;t be able to learn any kind of magic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「At this rate, I might even be forced to respawn from starving to death&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Doing that was even more shameful than being pummeled to death by basic mobs. I wouldn&rsquo;t be able to live with myself if that happened to me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When I was busy agonizing over my current predicament, I heard the voices of some other players around me for the first time in a while now. They were discussing some&hellip;&hellip; interesting stuff, to say the least.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Basically, if you buy the &ldquo;Flint Stone&rdquo; from any store inside of the game, you can forget about your problems with starting a fire or cooking. Pretty handy in certain situations.」</p>', 5, '2025-04-15 09:11:37', '2025-04-15 09:11:37');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(16, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 006', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-006', '<p>Chapter 6: A Wild Pervert Has Appeared!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was nothing wrong with hoarding your rations of meat in your inventory, but why would I even need about thirty pieces of meat if I couldn&rsquo;t even eat them?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!3\" data-google-query-id=\"CJSX6qKj2YwDFXJEwgUdLMUv3Q\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_2\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_2\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901972&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=185&amp;idt=124&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1005&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=3&amp;uci=a!3&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=128\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I decided to go in the direction of the voices, walking as fast as my over-encumbered status would allow me to.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「What about this one&hellip;&hellip; Aha, there it is!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I couldn&rsquo;t exactly see them in the tall grass they were in, but judging from the nametags above their heads they must have been players like me. There were two women and one man. They must have been a party that was grinding monsters together.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「A Knight, a Thief and a Sorceress&hellip;&hellip; Well-balanced party.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If my memory serves me correctly, Magicians would always start up with Fireball as their basic offensive spell. For some reason it was always the same in every single game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Summing up all of the raw ingredients I had on me right now it would give about seventy pieces, so if I offer them some they may be willing to share their fire with me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While I was thinking that, it seems that the party managed to encounter a monster on their path.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Uwah, what a cutie!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!4\" data-google-query-id=\"CK2q66Kj2YwDFbxEwgUdNqkmDw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_3\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_3\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901973&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=186&amp;idt=142&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1691&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=4&amp;uci=a!4&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=146\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cutie? Was there a cute monster out here aside from Orcs and Goblins?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「It looks just like a cute bunny&hellip;&hellip; But it must also be a monster.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fumu, the description would fit the Vorpal Bunny alright. Who would have thought that rare monster would spawn so frequently?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「This bunny, it&rsquo;s walking on two legs.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s definitely a Vorpal Bunny alright!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I stick my head into the grass and I can see a Sorceress that is approaching the Vorpal Bunny without a care in the world, while her companions stayed vigilant and guarded her. But looking at the Bunny, it was cracking its large head in a weird way. I knew it could only mean that it was readying itself to attack, but apparently they had no such knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Waaaaaaaaaiiiiiiiiittttttttt!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hee?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!5\" data-google-query-id=\"COiX7qKj2YwDFU1EwgUdEXA0AQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_4\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_4\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901974&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=187&amp;idt=152&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2401&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=5&amp;uci=a!5&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=156\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Huh?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Haa?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The party could see a half-naked man in a bird mask flying out of the tall grass while swinging his dual swords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I knew that it wasn&rsquo;t the best first impression out there, but I jumped in front of them, activating &ldquo;Flash Counter&rdquo; at the same time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Coming in between the Sorceress and the Vorpal Bunny, I manage to counter its attack and make my own, slashing at it neck with my swords.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I then spin around and slash with my left blade from the bottom all the way to the top of the Bunny&rsquo;s body, not giving it a moment to retaliate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My attack must have been a critical hit, for the Vorpal Bunny&rsquo;s HP drops to zero and it explodes in a geyser of pixels, leaving some drop behind him. While casting a quick glance at the loot I turn around to the three-people party that stood there dumbfounded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It looks like they needed a moment to comprehend what just happened.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!6\" data-google-query-id=\"CInA7KKj2YwDFWhFwgUdqy0t1g\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_5\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_5\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901975&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=188&amp;idt=163&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3087&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=6&amp;uci=a!6&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=166\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&hellip;&hellip; And what happened could be summarized as: &ldquo;a half-naked birdman jumped out of the tall grass and massacred a cute bunny.&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Kyaaaaaaaaahhhhhhhhh!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Iyaaaaaaaaahhhhhhhhh!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Uwaaaaaaaaahhhhhhhhh!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The three of them screamed in loud voices while raising their weapons in the air, ready to fight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Woah there, that&rsquo;s dangerous, you know!?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I said passively while the three players launched a simultaneous all-out attack in my direction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So I used my other skill &ldquo;Tap Step&rdquo; to put some distance in between us, trying to resolve the conflict with words rather than violence. It would be a good thing if they understood my intentions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CI6C8KKj2YwDFUZFwgUdhdkYmQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901976&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=188&amp;idt=173&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3773&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=5&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=177\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「STOP! STOP! STOP! STOP! STOP THAT!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Perverttttttttt!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Okay, yeah, right! I admit that my appearance is a little bit unusual, but look at my name tag! See!?I&rsquo;m a player, just like you! A player, God damn it!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Dieeeeeeeeee!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I wasn&rsquo;t against PVP in games like this, but I was against the idea of my very first PVP experience in this game to be something like that!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So I did my best to try to avoid the hits of the group. I repeated that action until the girl eventually started to calm down a little bit and stopped the other two.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Umm, this is&hellip;&hellip; Thank you very much for helping us out with that monster&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oh, it&rsquo;s no big deal, if I saw something like that at the very start of my adventuring I would certainly take such a person for a pervert as well&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CLeSiqOj2YwDFbFEwgUdbdEbeg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901977&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=190&amp;idt=182&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3040&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=8&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=654\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Once my status changed from the &ldquo;Perverted Birdhead&rdquo; to a &ldquo;Perverted Player with A Birdhead Sanraku&rdquo;, the party lowered their heads to me in an apologizing gesture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The boy knight&rsquo;s name was Soma, the thief girl was Kaho and the Sorceress was named Lina.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You could change many settings in the character creation, but the only thing that you were unable to change was your voice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That is why even the three people looked like young adults, from their voices I could kind of tell that they must have been Middle Schoolers at best.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I was kind of feeling sorry for scaring my juniors like that, but apparently they have never seen a mask like that before, hence the misunderstanding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Umm, this is, have you been always leveling up around these parts, Sanraku-san?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hm? Oh, yeah, I guess? I was originally going to see how the monsters behave around these parts, but it somehow happened that I stayed here and leveled up.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I guess one of my nasty habits from previous shitty games was surfacing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"1271867415\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CK6Bi6Oj2YwDFb5FwgUdROMj2w\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=1271867415&amp;adk=652191344&amp;adf=827654039&amp;pi=t.ma~as.1271867415&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693902&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693901977&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=190&amp;idt=187&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6214487042249&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=9&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3702&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95354563%2C95355311%2C95344791%2C95357878%2C95356808%2C95357716%2C95340252%2C95340254&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4142021605998595&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-005%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=9&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=662\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It was a habit of taking advantage of the places where monsters with good EXP values or rare items would spawn, which would allow me to go from one point to another while clearing the area over and over again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Please pardon me from spawn-camping the mobs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Basically there is little to no benefit to be had from not wearing any armor in this game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a result of that painful realization, there is always a bunch of half-naked players who want to buy the cheapest armor set possible, only to acquire at least some form of defense.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That is why if you want to gaze at half-naked avatars, you can only do this here, since you&rsquo;ll find them nowhere else. If you DO happen to encounter them, it is probably because of the following reasons:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&gt; They enjoy being seen half-naked by others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&gt; They enjoy taking huge amounts of damage, like any Massive Masochist would.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By the way, the protagonist is neither of the two. He&rsquo;s irregular in that regard.</p>', 6, '2025-04-15 09:12:04', '2025-04-15 09:12:04');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(17, 13, 'ShangriLa Frontier Chapter 007', 'shangrila-frontier-chapter-007', '<p>Chapter 7: Pervert Learns the Cost of Efficiency</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After I told the three people about my current predicament with too many items and no means to start a fire so that I could get rid of starvation&rsquo;s effect, they agreed to help me, also accepting the portion of the meat I willing to offer them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CNTIyL2j2YwDFetbDwIdMNYJIA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693956&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-007%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693956547&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=948&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=719922300181&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1029&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95344788%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2482214689644170&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=17\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Umm&hellip;&hellip; &ldquo;Fireball&rdquo;!!!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「「Ooh.」」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lina casts the spell and the moment it hits the branches we gathered around to start the fire, it changes them into a nice looking bonfire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Judging from their reactions and behavior, they must have been newbies at this game, just like me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oh, you can cook things in batches, huh&hellip;&hellip;? This game sure is convenient&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Umm, Sanraku&hellip; -san&hellip;&hellip;?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Just Sanraku is fine. After all, I am a ShanFro newbie, just like you guys. So we&rsquo;re pretty much on an equal footing here.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oh, really? I would have never been able to guess that, judging by your looks alone? Sanraku, why do you look like that&hellip;&hellip;?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CIWqyL2j2YwDFeJVDwIdhFoEJg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693956&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-007%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693956547&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=947&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=719922300181&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1691&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95344788%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2482214689644170&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=40\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lina seemed to be exhausted after casting the &ldquo;Fireball&rdquo; spell, so in the meantime I proposed to cook her batch of meat for her.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「In this game, you can sell your starting equipment as soon as the starting screen.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hm? Is that so!?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「That is why I sold basically everything else except for my weapons and headgear.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I see, but since the city is so close-by, couldn&rsquo;t you just buy and sell your equipment there?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The thief girl Kaho asked me that question, which made me understand that the initial spawn location must have also been randomized. When I told everyone where I was forced to start, they all looked at me sympathetically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「That&rsquo;s right&hellip;&hellip; What was that thing right there?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「You mean Vorpal Bunny?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CMurxr2j2YwDFTZWDwIdVX8yHg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693956&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-007%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693956547&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=947&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=719922300181&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2377&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95344788%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2482214689644170&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=48\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Yeah, yeah, is that Vorpal Bunny thing crazy strong or what?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hmm, let&rsquo;s see&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I might tell them what I know, but will they be able to do anything with that knowledge?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ultimately I decided to tell Soma, the boy who asked that question, that speed was crucial in dealing with Vorpal Bunny.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「If you aim at its neck fast enough, every single attack is supposed to be a critical hit, but it might be hard to hit a moving target with precision like that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「F, fast&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「It&rsquo;s a monster that initially seems hard, but is rather easy once you get used to dealing with it.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Just out of curiosity: what level are you, Sanraku?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!a\" data-google-query-id=\"COuzyL2j2YwDFc1bDwIdbSwgHA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693956&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-007%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693956547&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=947&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=719922300181&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3039&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95344788%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2482214689644170&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=10&amp;uci=a!a&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=55\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Level twelve. But the amount of EXP I&rsquo;m getting here is starting to dwindle a little bit, so I was thinking it might be good for me to find a new location to grind soon.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Ah, hunting like that&hellip;&hellip; But! It&rsquo;s been only a day since we started playing, so we still have so much possibilities to explore here!」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I think it would be a good idea to let these girls know that I&rsquo;m not your typical player when it comes to grinding and stuff like that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After all, the only thing that separates us is basically play time. It would be a different story if we started at around the same time, but in games like that overall play time was making all the difference.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「I went on a little break, and after that I went to grind into the forest for about seven hours or so. Thanks to that my inventory got so full and I was about to starve to death&hellip;&hellip;」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Aah, so that&rsquo;s why you needed some means to start a fire.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「That&rsquo;s right. And you really saved me out there&hellip;&hellip; For that, thank you very much.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to meat, the meat of the Vorpal Bunny seemed to be the one that was the best when cooked, and so I decided to distribute that one amongst our small group of people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!b\" data-google-query-id=\"CJafyL2j2YwDFc1fDwId5Eg6xg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693956&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-007%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693956547&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=947&amp;idt=1&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=719922300181&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3773&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95344788%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2482214689644170&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=11&amp;uci=a!b&amp;btvi=5&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=62\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Hmh&hellip;&hellip;!? It looks so good but it tastes so bland!?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In most games, even though you could eat many different things their taste would generally be pretty much the same (mostly tasting like pork, but there were some exceptions).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But much like in the real world, if you ate too much inside of the game you would be overcome with the urge to not want to do anything at all and just sleep, and in some cases to log out and eat some real food&hellip;&hellip; Good job, game. Good job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Ahh, now I want to eat some real meat.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「&hellip;&hellip;? If that&rsquo;s what you want to do, then why don&rsquo;t you just do it?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Nah, before I do that I want to get some more things done in this game.」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As I said that, the three of them nodded their heads in understanding.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I could log out anywhere and anytime I wanted, but in reality the safest thing to do would be to log out in a town or a safe zone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!c\" data-google-query-id=\"COfN7r6j2YwDFXpeDwIdC84ehw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_11\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_11\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744693960&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-007%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744693956550&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=951&amp;idt=1&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504100101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D2866bc2e90ef589f%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MZJACJoe2L3-LbLxHGKfExuw-Y61Q&amp;gpic=UID%3D0000109fcc9ed97a%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DALNI_MYMiu2FDS-_AnyTiWxU5ciKSufRGQ&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Db7c16eddc816c97c%3AT%3D1744692868%3ART%3D1744693692%3AS%3DAA-AfjZGlIQDT3K5bUpwaZn3B8th&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=719922300181&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=10&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3088&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95344788%2C95357877%2C95356808%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=2482214689644170&amp;tmod=1567802133&amp;uas=3&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fshangrila-frontier-shitty-games-hunter-challenges-godly-game%2Fshangrila-frontier-chapter-006%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=2&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=12&amp;uci=a!c&amp;btvi=8&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=4278\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For example, when I previously logged out to have a little break, after I came back, the tree that I was sitting on was almost broken in half and full of scratch marks. If I stayed there longer, I could have turned into nothing more than Goblin or Vorpal Bunny food.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>So I wanted to avoid doing that, so that I wouldn&rsquo;t have to brand this game as a shitty game as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>「Oh, that&rsquo;s right. I know this may sound stupid, but can I ask you some questions?」</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since they were to town before, I asked them about the shops that were located there, so that I could know where to best buy certain things. I also decided on making it a habit to scout out any new town that I would venture into as the first thing on my priority list.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since the three of them were on a gathering quest in the forest, we decided to go our separate ways from this point forward, with me going to the town which was the opposite of the direction they were going, to &ldquo;Secandill&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The main theme of this work is: &ldquo;overcoming the boundaries of the system with personal knowledge&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even when we have Person A and Person B, with their level, equipment, skills and game time being roughly the same, the one who has more knowledge about VR games in general is going to have the huge edge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And utilizing that knowledge can give you a tremendous boost when it comes to leveling up quickly, assembling your equipment or amassing a large sum of money&hellip;&hellip; That&rsquo;s just how it is.</p>', 7, '2025-04-15 09:12:51', '2025-04-15 09:12:51');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(18, 14, 'The Loner Who Conquers the Other World Chapter 1', 'the-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-chapter-1', '<p>Will the High School Boy who transports to Another World, Dream of a Deliveryman?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First Day &ndash; Classroom.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Reading a book.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s my usual routine during lunch break. Don&rsquo;t call me a loner! Although, I won&rsquo;t deny it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m surprised, the normies around me ~ have so many topics to talk about, it&rsquo;s impressive at this point. It&rsquo;s a second-year-class but all I can hear from their conversations is ridiculous. Despite all of that there was still a guy who was fiddling with his phone, who seemingly has not made any connections. To top it off, he sat in the middle of the classroom so he was subject to sounds from all around him, also there seemed to be more people in the classroom than usual. Why are you all gathering in this classroom? Was there something interesting here?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I continued to read. It would be fine to say that I started reading when I was a child. It started with picture books and then became all sorts of books.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You would assume that if you read this much then your eyesight will get worse but it won&rsquo;t worsen to the point where you would need glasses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My eyesight got worse because I&rsquo;m such a book addict? Mind your own business!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Regardless, it&rsquo;s sad that I can&rsquo;t focus on reading my book. In such a problem-filled class, why must a normal student like me be in it? Silence, be quiet, shut up you normies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Huh? Something is&hellip;here?&hellip;Coming? What is this feeling? Wait&hellip;huh!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The classroom floor began to shine, a circle and words combined with some geometric figure looking thing emits light&hellip;&hellip;wait, a magic formation? It&rsquo;s a magic formation. Ah&hellip;this is that.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Without a doubt. On the contrary, if this was some surprise math test, I would be more surprised at my math teacher.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By the time that thought came into my head, my body was already moving. Towards the back door, it won&rsquo;t open, I kick it but it does not break. I throw the chair near me at the window, it doesn&rsquo;t even crack.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CNaBo-KR2owDFbTJFgUdOUcl4A\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723563&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563186&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=793&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=1787&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=500&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=42\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indeed, so far it&rsquo;s as expected. I rush towards the locker in the back of the classroom, I open the tall locker used to store cleaning supplies. At the top, there is an inconspicuous hatch made for inspection. I use my momentum to slam my body against the hatch, nice. Then I jump towards the ceiling.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The radiance of the magic formation increased and finally, the entire classroom was enveloped by the white light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I crawled through the attic to get as far away as possible. Don&rsquo;t like it? But~, who cares about transferring to another world at this point. These days, light novels, anime, and manga are all about transportation to different worlds. Just leave it there, don&rsquo;t make real life about it too. Ah, just teleport the whole of Japan to a different world already. Ah, if a book about this was released then it would be interesting, I&rsquo;ll buy it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As things are like that, I continue crawling through the attic. I&rsquo;m already this far away so I should be fine&hellip;huuuuuh~.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uwahh, it actually happened. What a cliche turn of events!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a completely white room.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For it to be this cliche, this has truly surpassed my expectations. Don&rsquo;t tell me this is a swords and magic world. Is this some twisted space war or Sci-Fi world? I wouldn&rsquo;t want it to be a spiritual world or a horror world either.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, with the magic formation, it&rsquo;s probably not a Sci-Fi world? Then the world has connections to magic after all? No, no, that&rsquo;s probably not it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CMP3o-KR2owDFXvKFgUdw6Ae4A\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723563&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563186&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=793&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=2545&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=500&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=54\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Because of how well-known the genre of Isekai is nowadays, if someone were to say they transported to another world, it would be extremely embarrassing. The cliche development would be for him to meet God and be told that he would be transported to a world of swords and magic(lol). No matter what, he&rsquo;d be too embarrassed to say that right?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Was the magic formation a trap, and it was something scientific? What kind of world would that be? A math world? I really don&rsquo;t want to go to such a world!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Would the first enemy be factorization? I don&rsquo;t think I could win.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wait a moment, why isn&rsquo;t anyone here?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Are they out? Then don&rsquo;t summon me!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s basic equitique when inviting someone over&hellip;&hellip;(Long text complaining)<br />\r\n[1. TL Note: This is actually what the author put. I&rsquo;m not being lazy.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I think I&rsquo;m the type that takes my time reading. But it seems like I&rsquo;m fast at reading as many ask me whether I&rsquo;m properly reading it with how fast I flip pages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the books are light, it&rsquo;s easy to go through 20 of them in a single day. As such, I am already on my 4th book. I&rsquo;m going to eventually run out of books to read at this rate. Well, at least I brought my bag with me so I have books to read. In a quiet environment with enough light, that&rsquo;s not hot nor cold. It&rsquo;s the perfect environment for a reading addict like me. But man, nobody is coming, huh?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!a\" data-google-query-id=\"COLnpuKR2owDFSTIFgUdc9Mghw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723563&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563186&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=792&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=3327&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=500&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=10&amp;uci=a!a&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=99\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I wonder if I could buy any books somewhere here? I&rsquo;ll have God foot the bill.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hm, there&rsquo;s a grandpa here? He&rsquo;s looking over here. Is he lost? Grandpa, just because you&rsquo;re lost, doesn&rsquo;t mean you should come to another world. Don&rsquo;t tell me it&rsquo;s a story about a grandpa with dementia in another world!?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Why are you here?]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Grandpa, I already ate all the food&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[No you haven&rsquo;t!!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wait did he just read my thoughts!?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is that, when you&rsquo;re summoned into a white room, the man that appears, an old man with dementia that claims to be God.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Why-! The last part is uncalled for]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!b\" data-google-query-id=\"CNGYqOKR2owDFWzMFgUdpecjJg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723563&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563186&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=793&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723141%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=4013&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=500&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=11&amp;uci=a!b&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=123\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s an old man with fragile feelings, soon his blood vessels&hellip;will pop?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Don&rsquo;t go killing me off!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ah, an old man that scolds me for joking around&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Then stop fooling around! Listen to what I have to say seriously!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No, but they say that the type of people that say they don&rsquo;t want to fool around actually want to fool around, right? Well, I&rsquo;m sure there are also those that don&rsquo;t want to fool around as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Enough! I&rsquo;m not here to play games with you! Why are you here?]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uwah~, the guy summoned me here without my permission asks me what I&rsquo;m doing here? Old man with dementia confirmed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To top it off, he&rsquo;s listening to my thoughts without my permission and yelling at me.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!c\" data-google-query-id=\"CJT31eKR2owDFbzdFgUd-i49sg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_11\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_11\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723564&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563194&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=801&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=3583&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=500&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=12&amp;uci=a!c&amp;btvi=6&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=864\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>[I&rsquo;m done retorting!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Huh, is he snapping back at me?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Is this an Isekai story of an old man with dementia that screws people over? The title would be the [Demon Lord is actually an old man with dementia], something like that~.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Sigh~, can you seriously listen. The others that were summoned have already been teleported to the other world. Why are you still in this room?]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Well~you summoned everyone at the same time but I was the only one that you summoned to the wrong room?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Well, I summoned all you as a group not one by one. Meeting everyone I felt that perhaps one person was missing but to think there was one person summoned to the wrong room. You were the only one that was summoned to the wrong room.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Because of a certain person, I was brought here against my free will~? I do however have an idea of what happened.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[You do?! What did you&hellip;you escaped from the isolated space!? Huh, why is there an exit in the ceiling?]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"1271867415\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!d\" data-google-query-id=\"CLvP1uKR2owDFRvJFgUd0rMJpg\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_12\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_12\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=1271867415&amp;adk=652191344&amp;adf=827654039&amp;pi=t.ma~as.1271867415&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723564&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563194&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=801&amp;idt=1&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=4293&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=500&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=13&amp;uci=a!d&amp;btvi=7&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=877\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pupupu. The all-knowing deity of the heavens, our supreme and almighty God overlooked the maintenance hatch in the ceiling(LOL).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[How could I have known that-! How could I have known that rooms in your world have such an inconspicuous door in the ceiling. It would&rsquo;ve been weird if I knew!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More like, wasn&rsquo;t I safe after I was that far away? You lost sight of me so isn&rsquo;t that kind of cheating?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Like I already told you. You were only all summoned because of the compatibility of wavelengths between you all. If you were to run away alone, of course, the results would turn out as such. To top it all off, you&rsquo;re alone at the edge of the barrier and you don&rsquo;t even try to call out to me or reach me, and you&rsquo;re just reading books without a care in the world. Without paying either!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ah~, finally, you&rsquo;ve even read my memory, huh? Can we summon a forest while we&rsquo;re at it, for fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Don&rsquo;t summon something so large without permission. Moreover, if you do that each time a new volume comes out, a bookstore in that country will have to shut down. Consider how troublesome it is for the bookstore clerks!!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It didn&rsquo;t work, huh. Moreover, my mind was read too. Also, think about the troubles I have to go through as well! You&rsquo;re only thinking about the troubles of the bookstore clerks, did you receive a coupon or something? I want one too!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[I apologize but you were summoned to another world because of the wavelengths that you and your classmates share. This is the logic of the world. I didn&rsquo;t particularly choose you nor was I the one to summon you.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"8958785740\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!e\" data-google-query-id=\"CKGjueaR2owDFbfxFgUdQ9MdhA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_13\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_13\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=8958785740&amp;adk=3550488349&amp;adf=201824806&amp;pi=t.ma~as.8958785740&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723571&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723563197&amp;bpp=3&amp;bdt=804&amp;idt=3&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=3614705445776&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=16&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=23&amp;ady=4517&amp;biw=1442&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=718&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95331832%2C95353451%2C95354562%2C95354564%2C31091740%2C95357878%2C95357716%2C95340253%2C95340255&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=4042695285659753&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=3&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2F%3Ftab%3Dtable_contents&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1457%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1.32&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=14&amp;uci=a!e&amp;btvi=8&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=8779\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sh*t. I don&rsquo;t know what &lsquo;wavelengths&rsquo; you are talking about, but if the kids from other classes didn&rsquo;t barge into our classroom, we wouldn&rsquo;t have been summoned!?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>t wasn&rsquo;t bad enough interfering with my reading time so they prevented me from reading forever? I see, it all makes sense now, I was summoned to another world to defeat them?!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[No!! Don&rsquo;t arbitrarily decide that your classmates are the last boss and defeat them. That&rsquo;s just your personal grudge].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I will settle this grudge&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Listen to what I&rsquo;m saying-!].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ah~, hurry up then? Old people sure have a lot to say. Anyways the [(Self Proclaimed) God], is going to ask me to please go to a world of magic and swords (LOL). That&rsquo;s what you&rsquo;re planning on asking me anyways, isn&rsquo;t it?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CPqbge2R2owDFRJaDwIdFhoTzw\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723585&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723585725&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=606&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=7327252208636&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=17&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1053&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C31091740%2C95357877%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1050642314478732&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=21\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>[The [LOL] is unnecessary, also I&rsquo;m not self-proclaimed! Anyways, the others have already finished their preparations and left. If you don&rsquo;t hurry up, you&rsquo;ll be going to another world by yourself. You won&rsquo;t be able to meet up with those that went ahead at this rate. If you don&rsquo;t hurry up and prepare, they&rsquo;ll leave you behind].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ah~, the others, right. It&rsquo;s a real mess (LOL). The world is in the medieval period~, which means there won&rsquo;t be any books. After all, it&rsquo;s a mushroom kingdom, I&rsquo;ll have to hike through a dense forest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[You can&rsquo;t go hiking back! Your Isekai adventures will become full of only hiking!! Do you want an Isekai full of only hiking with the bookstore clerk!!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No, I just want to read books. Besides, why can&rsquo;t I go hiking with the bookstore clerk!?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s collect all the authors in one place, then summon them as a group&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Would you stop! Rather, I won&rsquo;t let you!]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The geezer&rsquo;s explanation was so long that I skipped it. He explained stuff about a kingdom, the other world&rsquo;s language, and demons. It&rsquo;s a long story so why not write it down? Although I want something to read, it doesn&rsquo;t seem like gramps has any literary talent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[All that&rsquo;s left is to prepare.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CJWggu2R2owDFdlgDwIdrBULjA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723585&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723585725&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=606&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=7327252208636&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=17&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1787&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C31091740%2C95357877%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1050642314478732&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=35\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What do I need to prepare? How many snacks am I allowed to bring with me or is there some other ridiculous problem I need to prepare for?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[You&rsquo;re going to choose a skill. First come, first served].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Old man&mdash;&mdash;-!!].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[I&rsquo;m telling you that I&rsquo;m God!! Who&rsquo;s the old man&ndash;!! You finally spoke for the first time but the first thing that you do is call me gramps?]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If 43 people choose before me that means that all the cheat skills are gone. The good skills were probably all taken, this is the worst. Gramps confirmed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Well, I might as well take a look&hellip;..</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Hurry up and choose a skill. To think there would come a day where I would become tired after becoming God].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, he got tired of retorting and continued the conversation by himself, so selfish. Ooo~oi&hellip;&hellip;not&hellip;&hellip;ah?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"COjQgu2R2owDFYBYDwIdcgkaVA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723585&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723585725&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=607&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=7327252208636&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=17&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2449&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C31091740%2C95357877%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1050642314478732&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=45\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Something that resembles a black plate floats in front of me, a lot of words are visible. Wouldn&rsquo;t a tablet have done the job? As expected, for the elderly, the newest technology is&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[I won&rsquo;t retort~, I won&rsquo;t retort anymore~.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He&rsquo;s whispering something under his breath, is he composing a poem?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Putting the foolish antics of the old man aside, I start reading at once, there&rsquo;s a large number of words. There are a lot of words but most of them are greyed out, does that mean they&rsquo;re taken?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the very top, [Status &ndash; Status Allocation, 1 point at a time dice (10P and two dice).] I currently have 50P. It&rsquo;s standard to put all your points into luck but I already have 10. Even if I dump all my points into it, it&rsquo;s only 60 which only feels so-so. I don&rsquo;t know if there&rsquo;s an upper limit nor if it will increase as I level up.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Allocate points to status, one at a time.] Why is this part the only part that&rsquo;s grey? I don&rsquo;t have any dice, I need 10P but I only have 2 dice, if there are six sides then the odds would be terrible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second one is [Item-weapon-armor-item 5P~50P], single-usage-consumable. 5P for medicine and poison antidotes. Weapons and armor range anywhere between 5P~30P and a set would cost 50P.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I want medicine so I don&rsquo;t die but it&rsquo;s not cost-efficient to buy. Perhaps I should purchase healing magic?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!a\" data-google-query-id=\"CPqhg-2R2owDFbhvDwIdPlwgig\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723585&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723585725&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=607&amp;idt=3&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=7327252208636&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=17&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3231&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C31091740%2C95357877%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1050642314478732&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=10&amp;uci=a!a&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=56\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are over 100 items but all that&rsquo;s left is [Assorted Items (Villager A) 50P]. [Holy Knight], [Great Sage], [Heavy Warrior], all at the great price of 50P but none are left. The only thing I can get is (Villager A) for 50P, this is way too unreasonable!! The set is composed of wooden sticks, clothes, and a diary of a villager.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The only good item left is these contact lenses which costs 30P. They improve your eyesight which can also help come off as more approachable. But 30P is too expensive!! Perhaps it&rsquo;s necessary if your eyesight is bad enough? There is a high possibility that the world won&rsquo;t have glasses as well. Regardless, 30P is impossible as I would only have 20P left no matter what.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The third category is [Martial Arts &ndash; 10P]. It is a reasonable and affordable price.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was also [Sword Arts], [Katana Arts], [Spear Arts], [Shield Arts], [Bow Arts], and [Whip Arts] but they&rsquo;re all sold out.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All that&rsquo;s left is [Cane Arts, become able to handle canes well &ndash; 10P]&hellip;I need a martial art and 10P is a reasonable price. Cane Arts&hellip;hit the enemy with a stick. Will that be enough to fight in another world? I&rsquo;m not a kid bullying a turtle at the beach. Then again, I couldn&rsquo;t even beat a turtle when I was a kid. Well, I&rsquo;d be sorry if I did.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, the 4th category, [Skill 10P~30P], it&rsquo;s expensive but&hellip;this is what I&rsquo;m talking about!! This is what a different world is, this is what I mean by cheats!! [Martial Arts experience UP], the standard [Magic], [Robbery], [Clairvoyance]. If it was cheap, these would be wonderful skills in another world&hellip;huh? None of them are left!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What&rsquo;s left is, hmm&hellip;what!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Less likely to catch a disease &ndash; 30P], yea this is perfectly fine. Rather, I want it! I&rsquo;m sure there won&rsquo;t be any hospitals. But it&rsquo;s 30P. This ability would be fine if it was a peaceful world. But it probably won&rsquo;t be so. If there are this many combat skills, there&rsquo;s no way that it would be a peaceful world, 30P is expensive. So that&rsquo;s why it was left.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!b\" data-google-query-id=\"CM6tlu2R2owDFZZXDwId-hUW0g\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723586&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723585729&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=610&amp;idt=2&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=7327252208636&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=17&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3200&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C31091740%2C95357877%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1050642314478732&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=11&amp;uci=a!b&amp;btvi=6&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=360\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Walking, become good at walking &ndash; 30P]. It might be good to have but who would buy this for 30P. [Martial Arts Experience Up], how is walking worth the same price as this? Do you summon things while walking? Nursery summons? Do heroes just walk at the Demon King? The Demon King sure will be scared~.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Still, that&rsquo;s one of the better ones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Gymnastics, become good at gymnastics &ndash; 30P]. Gymnastics debut in another world? Everyone~? It&rsquo;s over! It&rsquo;s seriously over.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The last horrifying skill is. It is&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Sensitive Body, turns your body into a sensitive body~ &ndash; 30P]. Don&rsquo;t mess around with me! A high school boy who&rsquo;s sensitive and feels good easily. Is this BL? Is it gay?<br />\r\n[1. TL Note: BL is short for boy&rsquo;s love. It refers to a genre of doujinshi where the plot is centered around love between guys.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I don&rsquo;t need this, I definitely don&rsquo;t need this. Still, half of those that were summoned are high school girls. None of them considered it? Well, there probably won&rsquo;t be any that would purchase it of their own volition, if someone did then please tell me. Please.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aren&rsquo;t you supposed to aim for one of the four great magics in times like these? Lightning, teleportation, healing&hellip;but there&rsquo;s nothing left. Wasn&rsquo;t choosing skills like this supposed to be an exciting event? Why am I crying? Why is God directing his eyesight away from me?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are four remaining. [Magic, [Temperature], adjust the temperature &ndash; 30P.] Ah, how convenient, should I aim to set up a food stall in another world? Did you think I&rsquo;d do that? There&rsquo;s no job like that in another world! Don&rsquo;t get mad!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!c\" data-google-query-id=\"CI2ome2R2owDFYNqDwIdGk8a8A\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_11\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_11\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2798401223&amp;adk=1918303987&amp;adf=3881259009&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2798401223&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723586&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723585732&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=613&amp;idt=1&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=7327252208636&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=17&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3703&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=4&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C31091740%2C95357877%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=1050642314478732&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-1%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=12&amp;uci=a!c&amp;btvi=7&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=404\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Only 3 remaining, [Magic, [Wrapping Magic], can wrap objects with magic &ndash; 30P]. What use is that? Will that call a delivery man? Does it summon them?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 remaining, [Magic, [Weight Magic], lowers or raises the weight of objects &ndash; 30P]. It lowers the weight of cargo and makes shipping cheaper! Looks like I have to summon the delivery man.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The last one is [Magic [Movement], auxiliary movement?&hellip;Decent I guess? Combined with the weight magic, you could probably get a job as a delivery man. Am I the one delivering?!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 5th category is [Special Abilities: 20P~50P]. Special abilities, special skills, sword talent, magic talent&hellip;required experience lowered, it can be combined with experience value increased, not that either is available. Nothing&rsquo;s left&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>First skill, [[Correspondent], communication, become good at consultations]. Is there a supervisor waiting for me in the other world? Salaryman in another world? If I level up will I become the president of a billion-dollar company?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The second skill, [[Jack of all trades], leveling up becomes slower]. Here it comes! A skill that is not useful at all and makes your life harder. Is it a trap? You&rsquo;re punished for accidentally clicking?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Last skill, [[Muppet, leveling becomes worse]. Terrible skill comes again! Again! What&rsquo;s the point of summoning people from another world if you&rsquo;re just going to make life harder for them.</p>', 1, '2025-04-15 17:26:47', '2025-04-15 17:40:59');
INSERT INTO `chapters` (`id`, `story_id`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `index`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(19, 14, 'The Loner Who Conquers in Another World Chapter 2', 'the-loner-who-conquers-in-another-world-chapter-2', '<p>Perhaps [Jack of All Trades] makes it harder to level up but it also makes it easier to learn skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, [Muppet] only makes it harder to level up? Does it possess some sort of mental ability? Can I make people listen to me? There&rsquo;s probably no mistake in deciding that this is the worst one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The last and 5th one is [Title 10P]. It&rsquo;s cheap but it&rsquo;s not very effective. The effectiveness of a title depends on its correlation with a job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, this may be more effective in the long-run compared to skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But more than anything [Sword Spirit, Guardian, Magician&hellip;]. Ahhhhhhhhhhhhhhh~! You can&rsquo;t tell me these are sold out too! Titles that shake my chuuni soul&hellip;even though I&rsquo;m a second year in high school. It&rsquo;s okay right, I&rsquo;m in a different world? Doesn&rsquo;t spirit sword sound pretty cool? It is pretty embarrassing to show it off. Well, good luck to the guy that took it.<br />\r\n[1. TN Note: Chuuni roughly translates to middle-grade syndrome. It&rsquo;s a way to describe those with delusional fantasies in puberty. He emphasizes that he&rsquo;s in high school because it&rsquo;s mainly used to describe those in middle school.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9144279732\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!7\" data-google-query-id=\"CLTC2PSR2owDFUSJ6QUdCFU4vQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_6\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_6\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9144279732&amp;adk=1602556744&amp;adf=573178662&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9144279732&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723601&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-3%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723601817&amp;bpp=2&amp;bdt=287&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6181841834222&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=18&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1125&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332924%2C31091740%2C95344788%2C95352053%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=701852304981262&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=7&amp;uci=a!7&amp;btvi=1&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=41\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I went through a stage where I thought of stuff like that too in the past. Even if it&rsquo;s embarrassing, shameful, or delusional, isn&rsquo;t it fine! At least compared to these two!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of them is [[Hikikomori], Your home will be protected]. Here comes the security guard killer, a NEET. Did they get kidnaped from their home and shoved into a different world? But your home is gone? Becoming a NEET in another world? There aren&rsquo;t any books though~. Wait&hellip;as long as a delivery man comes? But they won&rsquo;t come.<br />\r\n[2. TN Note: Hikikomori is a title given to those that stay within their homes and never leave. NEET stands for not in employment, education, or training. A person who is neither a student nor works.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The other one is [[NEET] All other jobs will become invalidated]. You&rsquo;d get defeated by demons before trying to work with this.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The end? The list of skills has reached its end or have I reached my end? Did this grandpa just sentence me to death?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Just what does he want me to do in another world?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[Hey~ why do you keep avoiding eye contact? Gramps, don&rsquo;t you have something to say to me? Make eye contact with me and properly say it.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After how much you rushed me to make preparations, you avoided looking at me as soon as the black plate with words appeared in front of me, right?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Not sure how much time has passed but when I look in front of me, gramps is on his knees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2251606319\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!8\" data-google-query-id=\"CKmV2_SR2owDFV2H6QUdby0JxA\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_7\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_7\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=2251606319&amp;adk=564636943&amp;adf=972325989&amp;pi=t.ma~as.2251606319&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723601&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-3%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723601817&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=287&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6181841834222&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=18&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=1859&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332924%2C31091740%2C95344788%2C95352053%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=701852304981262&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=8&amp;uci=a!8&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=74\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I intently harangue gramps to find out just what he wants me to do.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m not sure for what reason but you forcefully brought a normal high school student to another world. Whether that is God&rsquo;s will or the providence of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I thought there would be a reason for going that far, I thought there would be a justified reason, I thought there was no other choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, you can&rsquo;t expect a person that was suddenly kidnapped to understand. Even then, if you forcefully threw me into another world, there&rsquo;s probably nothing I can do.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s why you&rsquo;re giving me special skills right?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If there were no purpose, then there would be no reason to send us to another world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even if that was an accident, your duty as a God is to give us skills so that we can survive in another world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If it wasn&rsquo;t an accident and there was some reason for summoning me then at least give me the power to survive. That is the purpose of abilities and skills, to possess the potential to accomplish the goals we were summoned for.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5999279639\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!9\" data-google-query-id=\"CNWq2_SR2owDFdqG6QUd7TUSDQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_8\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_8\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=5999279639&amp;adk=2134429683&amp;adf=452700094&amp;pi=t.ma~as.5999279639&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723601&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-3%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723601817&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=286&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6181841834222&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=18&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2545&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332924%2C31091740%2C95344788%2C95352053%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=701852304981262&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=9&amp;uci=a!9&amp;btvi=3&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=81\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>What exactly do you wish to accomplish?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I show the list of skills very clearly to gramps. Is this the power necessary to survive in another world? Is this the power necessary to accomplish anything? Is this fulfilling your duty as God? Look carefully and tell me what you want me to do?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As gramps tries to make an excuse, I glare at him. As he tries to break his leg, I glare at him with a furious intensity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The gramps makes excuses with tears falling from his eyes and shaking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[So far, I&rsquo;ve only summoned at most 30 people so there were more than enough skills to choose from.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There were a lot of instances where people wouldn&rsquo;t monopolize everything as it would come back to bite them in the ass.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If a whopping 43 people come, even if the latter people will be troubled, they take it all for themselves.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was never a case similar to yours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"9746952951\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!a\" data-google-query-id=\"CNTn2_SR2owDFUyt6QUdJv0OoQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_9\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_9\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=9746952951&amp;adk=3510032111&amp;adf=2613040719&amp;pi=t.ma~as.9746952951&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723601&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-3%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723601817&amp;bpp=4&amp;bdt=287&amp;idt=4&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6181841834222&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=18&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=3231&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332924%2C31091740%2C95344788%2C95352053%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=701852304981262&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=10&amp;uci=a!a&amp;btvi=4&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=91\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, all of the skills here have been recognized by me as skills that have accomplished something worthy of praise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Skills are things that have been recognized by God, become God, and overcame God. They are remnants of a soul.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Skills are souls, a way of living, and memories.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And because they have surpassed God, they are something that not even God can understand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gaining those skills, you feel their soul, understand the lives they&rsquo;ve led, you receive those feelings to activate those skills. That is the type of power it is. And all the skills that exist right now have already been activated and have achieved something.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To remember, feel, and understand, that is what a true skill is. If you&rsquo;re unable to do that then no matter how powerful a skill it is, it becomes useless, a hindrance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The things here are certainly, things that I do not understand, things that I&rsquo;ve never seen before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But just by the fact that they are here, they have a meaning, purpose, and they are necessary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"6670692468\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><iframe allow=\"attribution-reporting; run-ad-auction\" allowtransparency=\"true\" aria-label=\"Advertisement\" browsingtopics=\"true\" data-google-container-id=\"a!b\" data-google-query-id=\"COHI9_SR2owDFVSI6QUd_eoAXQ\" data-load-complete=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_10\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_10\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?gdpr=0&amp;us_privacy=1---&amp;gpp_sid=-1&amp;client=ca-pub-6973349055852983&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;slotname=6670692468&amp;adk=1146076604&amp;adf=1608662326&amp;pi=t.ma~as.6670692468&amp;w=1030&amp;abgtt=6&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1744723602&amp;rafmt=1&amp;format=1030x280&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-3%2F&amp;fwr=0&amp;fwrattr=true&amp;rpe=1&amp;resp_fmts=3&amp;wgl=1&amp;uach=WyJXaW5kb3dzIiwiMTAuMC4wIiwieDg2IiwiIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSIsbnVsbCwwLG51bGwsIjY0IixbWyJHb29nbGUgQ2hyb21lIiwiMTM1LjAuNzA0OS44NSJdLFsiTm90LUEuQnJhbmQiLCI4LjAuMC4wIl0sWyJDaHJvbWl1bSIsIjEzNS4wLjcwNDkuODUiXV0sMF0.&amp;dt=1744723601826&amp;bpp=1&amp;bdt=296&amp;idt=-M&amp;shv=r20250410&amp;mjsv=m202504140101&amp;ptt=9&amp;saldr=aa&amp;abxe=1&amp;cookie=ID%3D01025ce41beeef37%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MZ2NCoeUPoOY_1yJ1hcKIcaTyADGA&amp;gpic=UID%3D000010a012dba8ca%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DALNI_MYRL0kqEbb0pK7vrEL5ZMwwD40Z_w&amp;eo_id_str=ID%3Dc538dd61eebec506%3AT%3D1744723141%3ART%3D1744723564%3AS%3DAA-AfjblR72zy6EtY-LQ3hUu2Odz&amp;prev_fmts=0x0%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C1030x280%2C336x280%2C336x280%2C336x280&amp;nras=1&amp;correlator=6181841834222&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;u_tz=420&amp;u_his=18&amp;u_h=1080&amp;u_w=1920&amp;u_ah=1040&amp;u_aw=1920&amp;u_cd=24&amp;u_sd=1&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=255&amp;ady=2801&amp;biw=1905&amp;bih=953&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=20&amp;eid=95355973%2C95355975%2C95332924%2C31091740%2C95344788%2C95352053%2C95357716&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=701852304981262&amp;tmod=1899943773&amp;uas=0&amp;nvt=1&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Flightnovelstranslations.com%2Fnovel%2Fthe-loner-who-conquers-the-other-world-wn%2Fvolume-1-chapter-1-part-2%2F&amp;fc=1920&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1920%2C0%2C1920%2C1040%2C1920%2C953&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7CeEbr%7C&amp;abl=CS&amp;pfx=0&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;bz=1&amp;td=1&amp;tdf=2&amp;psd=W251bGwsW251bGwsbnVsbCxudWxsLCJkZXByZWNhdGVkX2thbm9uIl0sbnVsbCwxXQ..&amp;nt=1&amp;pgls=CAEaBTYuNy4y~CAA.&amp;ifi=11&amp;uci=a!b&amp;btvi=6&amp;fsb=1&amp;dtd=529\" tabindex=\"0\" title=\"Advertisement\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"1030\"></iframe></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Which is why they are here at this time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He pleads while crying, his legs shaking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He&rsquo;s trying to explain while standing up but his legs are like a newborn deer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is bad, gramps, my eyes hurt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Is it something like that? The soul of a passionate tennis player somehow entered gramps? It&rsquo;s that bad. It&rsquo;s just so bad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That skill is just too dangerous, this sight is something that even surpasses God, it&rsquo;s crossed a line that it shouldn&rsquo;t cross. It&rsquo;s some sort of soul or a form of spirituality, anyways gramps, run away~.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>[As God, my duty to truth, reason, and providence, I shall surpass them both].</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ya~ba~i~, gramps is broken!! I said you shouldn&rsquo;t have crossed that line.<br />\r\n[3. TN Note: &ldquo;Yabai&rdquo; means it&rsquo;s bad. It&rsquo;s a phrase that young people use in Japan and it&rsquo;s kind of similar to saying &lsquo;sh*t&rsquo;.]</p>\r\n\r\n<p><ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6973349055852983\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2798401223\" data-ad-status=\"unfilled\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"><ifram